\tr 
\tc1 Kolosi 2:9-10
\tc2 Hibru 1:1-14
\tc3 Rom 1:3-4
\tr 
\tc1 2 Korin 4:4-6
\tc2 Luk 1:26-38
\tc3 Galesia 4:4-5
\tr 
\tc1 Matyu 16:13-17
\tc2 Jon 5:19-29
\tc3 Jon 6:35-40
\tr 
\tc1 Jon 11:25-27
\tc2 Jon 14:5-11
\tc3 Jon 17:1-5
\tr 
\tc1 Jon 20:26-31
\tc2 Aposel 3:13-16
\tc3 Aposel 4:10-12
\tr 
\tc1 1 Jon 2:1-2
\tc2 1 Jon 5:20
\tc3 Uli Anjam 19:11-16
\p 
\v 3 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “Qotei a e qa are qalosaieqnu.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:
\tr 
\tc1 1 Jon 4:9-10
\tc2 Rom 5:8
\tc3 Jon 3:16
\tr 
\tc1 1 Timoti 2:3-6
\tc2 2 Pita 3:9
\tc3 
\p 
\v 4 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “E une saiqoji.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:
\tr 
\tc1 Rom 3:10-12, 23-24
\tc2 Rom 5:12
\tc3 Galesia 3:22
\tr 
\tc1 1 Jon 1:8-10
\tc2 Jon 3:18-20, 36
\tc3 Aposel 17:30-31
\tr 
\tc1 Kolosi 3:5-10
\tc2 Rom 6:23
\tc3 Galesia 6:7-8
\tr 
\tc1 2 Tesalonaika 1:7-9
\tc2 1 Pita 4:3-5
\tc3 Uli Anjam 20:11-15
\p 
\v 5 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “Qotei na ijo une kobotqasai.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:
\tr 
