\tr 
\tc1 1 Timoti 1:15-16
\tc2 Hibru 10:17-18
\tc3 1 Jon 1:8-10
\p 
\v 6 Ino areqalo qujai agi Yesus Kristus na ni oqajqa. Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:
